  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810770/extras/c6a6c47f844dbcce9b96ceae8cd460b6.apng?t=1741323621\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810770/extras/c6a6c47f844dbcce9b96ceae8cd460b6.poster.avif?t=1741323621\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=60 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on your destiny of becoming a Realmweaver, a powerful wizard with the ability to open gates and travel between realms to uncover the mysteries of the universe. Travel across a realm left in ruins and return it to its former beauty!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810770/extras/22b7cb138f37f8c3afba0a687c033647.apng?t=1741323621\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810770/extras/22b7cb138f37f8c3afba0a687c033647.poster.avif?t=1741323621\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=60 /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+ Puzzles To Solve</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 Unique Chapters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stylized Isometric Pixel-Art Graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secrets/Collectibles To Find</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interesting Characters and Storyline</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WASD or Arrow Key Movement</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Achievements</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810770/extras/e3e496a68a43e1b2237876a1f48fe4cc.apng?t=1741323621\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810770/extras/e3e496a68a43e1b2237876a1f48fe4cc.poster.avif?t=1741323621\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=60 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have everyone enjoy the game!</p>",
